<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Recovery Request Denied</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #222;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      p {
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Account Recovery Request Denied</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= fullname %>,</p>
      <p>
        We regret to inform you that your account recovery request has been
        denied. After careful consideration, we are unable to restore your
        account at this time.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you believe this decision was made in error, or if you have any
        questions, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The HTU LMS Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
